snippet.title: The Hero of Dreams Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The Hero of Dreams official Trailer!!! This is my game, This is a free game and every Zelda fan is welcome to play it. It is around 20+ hours long and it is getting a lot of acclaim. Again, all I ask is to please subscribe to my channel if you download the game, and thank you for the support!

Here is the download video:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9P1XYS2yTWQ

And T-shirts!!!!
